# topology.sakmath - Sakum symbolic mathematics: Topology
# domain=Mathematics/Topology  format=sakmath

# --- Open sets ---
खुला_समुच्चय U ⊆ X   ⇔   (∀ x ∈ U)(∃ ε>0)(B_ε(x) ⊆ U)

# --- Continuous ---
संतत f: X→Y   ⇔   (∀ V खुला ⊆ Y)(f^{-1}(V) खुला ⊆ X)

# --- Homeomorphism ---
गृहसमरूपता f: X→Y जो बिजेक्टिव, संतत, और f^{-1} भी संतत

# --- Fundamental group ---
मूल_समूह π_1(X, x0) = {लूप at x0 under समरूपता}

# self-test hook
परीक्षा {
  लेख "topology.sakmath loaded"
}
